              <object>
                <lexicalForm>For want of a better class name: denotes the rolling stock (locos, wagons...) AND their supplies (possibly depleted) AND their (variable) loads, considered as a whole, i.e. whatever is moved somewhere between origin and destination in a Train run.</lexicalForm>
