                <lexicalForm>ILU code (under EN 13044 series) is the standardized identification (owner, number, check digit) for intermodal loading units in Europe. The ILU code is designed for non-ISO containers, swap bodies, semi-trailers in intra-European combined transport.</lexicalForm>
